#  To-Do List App

A simple and responsive To-Do List web application built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** to manage daily tasks efficiently.


##  Live Demo

 https://reinachaturvedi09-lgtm.github.io/todo-list-app


##  Features

*  Add new tasks
*  Mark tasks as completed (click on task)
*  Delete tasks
*  Saves tasks using Local Storage
*  Clean and modern dark UI



##  Tech Stack

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript


##  Project Structure

todo-list-app/
│── index.html
│── assets/
│   └── screenshot.png
